# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Big Brother — Required Secrets
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add these in your repo under:
# Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions → New repository secret

# 1. Your Anthropic API key
#    Get one at: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# The following are auto-provided by GitHub Actions.
# You do NOT need to add these manually.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# GITHUB_TOKEN  → injected automatically by GitHub
# PR_BODY       → pulled from the pull request event payload
